field.value:
generator.CreateInterfaceProxyWithoutTarget( typeof( IFoo ), new[] { typeof( IBar ), typeof( IBaz ) } );
generator.CreateInterfaceProxyWithoutTarget( typeof( IFoo ), new[] { typeof( IBaz ), typeof( IBar ) } );

These two calls will generate two proxy types which will obviously be semantically identical. Instead caching mechanism should be order independent. This should also include inherited interfaces.

